<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <title>BlaKats | Pure Heart</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Stream Pure Heart and support BlaKats with direct downloads." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #050505;
      --panel: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --panel-strong: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      --text: #f5f5f5;
      --muted: #b6b6b6;
      --accent: #c08a1a;
      --accent-2: #f1b93a;
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      --radius: 22px;
      --max: 1200px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1a1a1a 0%, #090909 30%, #040404 100%);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { display: block; max-width: 100%; }

    .topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 30;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      background: rgba(5,5,5,0.68);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .topbar-inner {
      max-width: var(--max);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .brand-badge {
      width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      color: #111;
      font-weight: 900;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .nav a:hover { color: #fff; }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 13px 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: transform .2s ease, opacity .2s ease, background .2s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      color: #111;
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-color: var(--line);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.35), rgba(0,0,0,0.88)),
        url('img/pexels-cottonbro-6892708.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
      transform: scale(1.04);
      filter: saturate(0.85);
    }

    .hero-inner {
      position: relative;
      max-width: var(--max);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 56px 20px 44px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 28px;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 78vh;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.7rem, 5vw, 5rem);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .hero-copy p {
      max-width: 60ch;
      color: #e3e3e3;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 18px 0 26px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hero-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      max-width: 620px;
    }

    .stat {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .stat strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .stat span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .player-card {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 26px;
      background: rgba(12,12,12,0.78);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .player-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .player-label {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .player-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .pill {
      white-space: nowrap;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
    }

    .video-shell {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 22px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #000;
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .video-shell video,
    .video-shell .video-poster {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .video-shell video {
      display: none;
      background: #000;
    }

    .video-shell.loaded video {
      display: block;
    }

    .video-shell.loaded .video-poster {
      display: none;
    }

    .video-poster {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.15), rgba(0,0,0,0.7)),
        url('img/pexels-davis-sanchez-3916376.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .poster-overlay {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 26px;
    }

    .play-btn {
      width: 86px;
      height: 86px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: none;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.94);
      color: #111;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .poster-caption {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    }

    .player-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    .player-note {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    .section {
      max-width: var(--max);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 56px 20px;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: end;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .section-head h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .section-head p {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 60ch;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .video-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .tile {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .tile-thumb {
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #121212, #232323);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .tile-body {
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .tile-body h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }

    .tile-body p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .split {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .panel {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .panel h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .panel p,
    .panel li {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .qr-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 18px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .qr-title {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
    }

    .qr-img {
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: #fff;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--muted);
      padding: 26px 20px 40px;
    }

    .footer-inner {
      max-width: var(--max);
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero-inner,
      .split,
      .video-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero {
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .hero-stats {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .nav { display: none; }
      .topbar-inner { padding: 12px 16px; }
      .hero-inner { padding: 34px 16px 30px; }
      .section { padding: 42px 16px; }
      .section-head { align-items: start; flex-direction: column; }
      .qr-img { width: 190px; height: 190px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <script>
    const PAYMENT_URL = "https://hicommission.github.io/music-portfolio/index.html";
    const DOWNLOAD_URL = "https://hicommission.github.io/music-portfolio/index.html";
    const R2_BASE = "https://YOUR_R2_PUBLIC_BASE_URL";

    const PURE_HEART_VIDEO = {
      desktop: R2_BASE + "/PureHeart_web_copy.mp4",
      mobile: R2_BASE + "/PureHeart_web_mobile.mp4",
      title: "Pure Heart",
      subtitle: "Exclusive BlaKats feature video"
    };

    function qrImageUrl(forUrl) {
      return "https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=220x220&data=" + encodeURIComponent(forUrl);
    }

    function isMobileDevice() {
      return window.matchMedia("(max-width: 820px)").matches ||
        /Android|iPhone|iPad|iPod|Opera Mini|IEMobile|Mobile/i.test(navigator.userAgent) ||
        (navigator.connection && navigator.connection.saveData);
    }

    function pickBestVideoSource() {
      return isMobileDevice() ? PURE_HEART_VIDEO.mobile : PURE_HEART_VIDEO.desktop;
    }

    function initVideoHero() {
      const shell = document.getElementById("pureheart-video-shell");
      const video = document.getElementById("pureheart-video");
      const source = document.getElementById("pureheart-video-source");
      const poster = document.getElementById("pureheart-poster");
      const debug = document.getElementById("pureheart-debug");
      if (!shell || !video || !source || !poster) return;

      let loaded = false;

      const doLoad = () => {
        if (loaded) return;
        loaded = true;
        source.src = pickBestVideoSource();
        video.load();
        shell.classList.add("loaded");
        if (debug) debug.textContent = "";
      };

      const doLoadAndPlay = async () => {
        doLoad();
        try {
          await video.play();
        } catch (err) {
          if (debug) debug.textContent = "Video loaded. Tap play in the controls if autoplay is blocked.";
        }
      };

      poster.addEventListener("click", doLoadAndPlay);
      poster.addEventListener("keypress", (e) => {
        if (e.key === "Enter" || e.key === " ") {
          e.preventDefault();
          doLoadAndPlay();
        }
      });

      video.addEventListener("error", () => {
        if (debug) debug.textContent = "Video failed to load. Check R2 public URL, filename, or bucket permissions.";
      });

      if ("IntersectionObserver" in window) {
        const io = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
          entries.forEach((entry) => {
            if (entry.isIntersecting) {
              doLoad();
              io.disconnect();
            }
          });
        }, { rootMargin: "260px 0px" });
        io.observe(shell);
      } else {
        doLoad();
      }
    }

    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      const qrImg = document.getElementById("purchase-qr-img");
      const payLink = document.getElementById("purchase-link");
      const payLink2 = document.getElementById("purchase-link-2");
      const dl = document.getElementById("download-url");

      if (qrImg) qrImg.src = qrImageUrl(PAYMENT_URL);
      if (payLink) payLink.href = PAYMENT_URL;
      if (payLink2) payLink2.href = PAYMENT_URL;
      if (dl) dl.textContent = DOWNLOAD_URL;

      initVideoHero();
    });
  </script>

  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="topbar-inner">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="brand-badge">B</div>
        <div>BlaKats x HiCommission</div>
      </div>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="#watch">Watch</a>
        <a href="#highlights">Highlights</a>
        <a href="#download">Download</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <a href="https://hicommission.github.io/music-portfolio/index.html" class="btn btn-primary">Buy a Download</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero" id="watch">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <div class="eyebrow">Now Streaming • Pure Heart</div>
        <h1>Pure Heart.<br>Front and center.</h1>
        <p>
          A premium BlaKats landing page built to feel cinematic, play fast, and guide fans straight to your download flow.
          The hero auto-selects the best video for desktop or mobile and stays lightweight until it enters view.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#player" class="btn btn-primary">Watch Now</a>
          <a href="https://hicommission.github.io/music-portfolio/index.html" class="btn btn-secondary">Buy the Download</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stats">
          <div class="stat"><strong>Mobile-aware</strong><span>Serves the lighter file on phones and tablets.</span></div>
          <div class="stat"><strong>Lazy-loaded</strong><span>Loads video only when it matters for better performance.</span></div>
          <div class="stat"><strong>Cloudflare-ready</strong><span>Works with your R2 public URL and CDN edge delivery.</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="player-card" id="player">
        <div class="player-head">
          <div>
            <div class="player-label">Featured video</div>
            <h2 class="player-title">Pure Heart</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="pill">Exclusive stream</div>
        </div>

        <div id="pureheart-video-shell" class="video-shell">
          <div id="pureheart-poster" class="video-poster" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Load and play Pure Heart video">
            <div class="poster-overlay">
              <button class="play-btn" aria-hidden="true">▶</button>
              <div style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:800;">Pure Heart</div>
              <div class="poster-caption">Tap to load and play</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <video id="pureheart-video" controls playsinline preload="none" controlsList="nodownload">
            <source id="pureheart-video-source" src="" type="video/mp4">
            Your browser does not support HTML5 video.
          </video>
        </div>

        <div class="player-actions">
          <div class="player-note" id="pureheart-debug">Optimized for fast first paint and clean playback.</div>
          <a href="https://hicommission.github.io/music-portfolio/index.html" class="btn btn-primary">Buy a Download</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="highlights">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <h2>Why this page converts better</h2>
        <p>Put your strongest video first, reduce distractions, and give visitors a straight line from watch to purchase.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="video-grid">
      <article class="tile">
        <div class="tile-thumb">Hero-first layout</div>
        <div class="tile-body">
          <h3>Pure Heart stays above the fold</h3>
          <p>Your main video is the first thing people see instead of getting buried beneath older sections.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="tile">
        <div class="tile-thumb">Streaming feel</div>
        <div class="tile-body">
          <h3>Spotify / Netflix-inspired presentation</h3>
          <p>Dark cinematic visuals, stronger hierarchy, and cleaner calls to action make the page feel more premium.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="tile">
        <div class="tile-thumb">Faster load</div>
        <div class="tile-body">
          <h3>Performance-conscious</h3>
          <p>Video loads near the viewport, YouTube embeds can remain lower on the page, and mobile users get the lighter file.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section split" id="download">
    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Direct support</h3>
      <p>
        Hi BlaKats fans! Lead vocalist Hollywood, composer and guitarist G-Funk, plus producer and rapper MeloDee Man,
        want to use this platform to connect directly with you and sell music without extra middle layers.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our mission is to record and release CDs and singles online while building a more direct fan relationship.
        Support the movement by purchasing an official download.
      </p>
      <a href="https://hicommission.github.io/music-portfolio/index.html" class="btn btn-primary">Buy a Download</a>
    </div>

    <div class="qr-card">
      <div class="qr-title">Scan to Buy & Download</div>
      <a id="purchase-link" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <img id="purchase-qr-img" class="qr-img" alt="QR code for music purchase" src="" loading="lazy" />
      </a>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;">Scan the QR code to open the payment page. After payment, redirect to your download destination.</p>
      <div style="margin-top:14px;">
        <a id="purchase-link-2" class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open Payment Page</a>
      </div>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.92rem;margin-top:14px;">Configured download destination: <span id="download-url"></span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section split">
    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Studio scene</h3>
      <p>Keep your original YouTube content as supporting material below the hero, where it still adds credibility without stealing focus.</p>
      <iframe width="100%" height="315"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ugOvYObkal8?start=12"
        title="YouTube video player"
        frameborder="0"
        loading="lazy"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>

    <div class="panel" id="contact">
      <h3>Contact & collaboration</h3>
      <p>We want to link up with others and launch new music projects. Reach out if you want to collaborate, license, or support.</p>
      <p><a href="mailto:gsizzler@gmail.com">gsizzler@gmail.com</a></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Independent music distribution</li>
        <li>Direct-to-fan support</li>
        <li>New music and visual rollouts</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <div>Hicommission Music</div>
      <div>Project by <a href="https://hicommission.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hicommission Music</a></div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>